WEBVTT

00:01.069 --> 00:04.505
Aaron, I mean this
from the very bottom of my heart.

00:04.672 --> 00:05.730
I love you.

00:05.907 --> 00:07.067
Nice try.

00:07.242 --> 00:10.473
I've gotten more emotion
out of my car's navigational system.

00:10.645 --> 00:12.806
You know, I knew it was childish
to practice on my cat.

00:12.981 --> 00:14.471
I should be doing this in the mirror.

00:14.649 --> 00:16.480
And in fact, I'll do it one better.

00:17.886 --> 00:20.184
Aaron, I've been wanting
to tell you this for a long time.

00:20.355 --> 00:21.788
I love you.

00:21.956 --> 00:23.856
Aw, that's great, Sabrina. Thanks.

00:24.025 --> 00:25.617
Oh, no, no, no.
Not the dreaded thanks.

00:25.793 --> 00:28.353
- Try again. I love you.
- Ditto.

00:28.530 --> 00:30.521
No. No "ditto." No "right back at you."

00:30.698 --> 00:32.631
No, "yeah, same to you,
but more of it."

00:32.800 --> 00:35.428
- Just tell me you love me.
- I love you.

00:35.970 --> 00:38.700
Oh, well, that's really sudden,
but, heh...

00:40.275 --> 00:41.708
...I love you too.

00:46.981 --> 00:49.245
What? I look hot today.

00:51.000 --> 00:57.074
